  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "The Ledger Live app (https://www.ledger.com/pages/ledger-live) displays the path that MyCrypto uses as \"Ethereum Classic 1 (legacy)\" (`\"freshAddressPath\": \"44'/60'/160720'/0'/0\",` when you click on the settings icon in Ledger Live).\r\n\r\nThe default Ethereum Classic path on Ledger Live is `\"freshAddressPath\": \"44'/61'/0'/0/0\",`, which doesn't seem to be supported by MyCrypto.",
